    <h3>Importing Solana Wallets</h3>
    <p>Most tools allow you to import wallets by:</p>
    <ol>
        <li><strong>Public address import:</strong> Connect your Phantom/Solflare/Backpack address. The tool reads all transaction history via Solana RPC.</li>
        <li><strong>API key import (exchanges):</strong> Connect Binance, Coinbase, Kraken, or other CEX accounts via API for automated transaction syncing.</li>
        <li><strong>CSV upload:</strong> For wallets that can't be programmatically accessed, most tools accept CSV exports.</li>
        <li><strong>Direct RPC node:</strong> Advanced users can connect their own RPC endpoint for faster and more complete data extraction.</li>
    </ol>

